on his own merits?

1108
01:02:45,139 --> 01:02:46,557
He's an idiot.

1109
01:02:46,641 --> 01:02:48,226
Makes no sense.

1110
01:02:49,769 --> 01:02:51,562
Watch your fucking tone, Captain.

1111
01:02:51,646 --> 01:02:53,773
Whoa, whoa, whoa.

1112
