what the hell is going on?

1169
01:08:22,727 --> 01:08:24,103
I mean Tweedy is dead.

1170
01:08:24,186 --> 01:08:25,646
I'm sorry to hear it.

1171
01:08:26,480 --> 01:08:27,690
