1216
01:10:49,749 --> 01:10:51,459
Felicia, the board decided...

1217
01:10:51,542 --> 01:10:53,169
Don't give me that shit.

1218
01:10:53,252 --> 01:10:54,211
Beg your pardon?

1219
01:10:54,295 --> 01:10:55,713
I can't believe
you're dragging your feet,

1220
01:10:55,796 --> 01:10:58,591
